Mission & Values

Driven by a commitment to people-first solutions and social equity, I believe in building systems that prioritize the wellbeing of every community member. Through my work in policy research, legal advocacy, and community service, I strive to create meaningful change that makes essential services accessible and affordable for all. My approach centers on collaboration, evidence-based decision-making, and a steadfast belief that everyone deserves the opportunity to live their best life.
